Remarks.
This new species resembles 

M. macrosolenus

for having small dorsal setae and strong striae on its idiosoma. It differs from this species as it has serrated trichobothria (
bo
) instead of plumose trichobothria (
bo
) and it has an irregular reticulated prodorsum (reticulation absent in 

M. macrosolenus

).
